{"type": "article", "id": 20904, "title": "咖啡豆和咖啡罐设计", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-19T07:30:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702164747nOETzAkqwB2f87iN.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是韩国设计工作室 ahhaproject 带来的装咖啡豆的罐子设计，目前还是一个概念。他们将速溶咖啡粉做成一种“咖啡豆”，想让溶解咖啡豆成为一种喝咖啡的方式，既能避免拆袋的浪费，也能节约时间。外面的罐子则干净素雅，一个大脸娃娃头增添了梦幻和卡通的色彩，令人感到轻松愉悦。而娃娃头上的咖啡豆则点出了产品本身的设计。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150653CQ04jFtH2vEzTrxo.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"630\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.58333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150654i7aDJkUYCBcRrWtb.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"799\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150655rCDOVyuilpQ0jwGZ.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"678\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150655UmErFHeynO8SN04R.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1099\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.01759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150656XqoGpEi6VnhDCuUS.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1152\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.06666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}